WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
In the winter wilderness of the Soviet mountains, nine hikers vanished into a mystery that still survives.

00:06.000 --> 00:12.000
Their camp, belongings, and final movements raised more questions than answers.

00:12.000 --> 00:20.000
This story follows the evidence, the theories, and the fear surrounding Dyatlov Pass.
